name: Sufuraamathi
overview:
Sufuraamathi, meaning dinner table in English, is the one and only third party food delivery service provider in the Maldives,

We pride ourselves on a number of things: Express Food Delivery Lowest Price in Town The First Free Delivery Service in Town Friendly Staffs Widest variety of cuisines, dishes and restaurants to chose from

Our customers are able to place orders at the comfort of their homes or offices with a few simple clicks to satisfy their hunger or cravings

We partner with some of the largest and most well-known restaurants and cafes in town and offer their dishes to our customers at their menu prices so that our customers get to enjoy humanities very basic necessity at the most affordable prices

So log into www.sufuraamathi.com and chose your order from over 150 different dishes from 7 different restaurants
